songs.title: Believe (Unreleased)
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
It's like every time you fall
No one's gonna lend you a helping hand, oh
Wondering will you spend your life facing four walls
Like standing in quicksand, oh

[Pre-Chorus]
Don't let your guard down, hold your head up
Life comes at you fast, gotta stay strong
I know what you can be cause underneath
You've had wings all along

[Chorus]
And you've been travelling the same road for a long time
Feels like you're burning rubber going nowhere fast
I mean to tell you there's no limit to what you can do
You just gotta believe
